40,"uid":77362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:24:56.000Z","msg":"そばにいたいよ<br />\n只想留在你身邊<br />\n君きみのために出来できることが&nbsp;僕ぼくにあるかな<br />\n為了你 我能做些什麼呢<br />\nいつも君きみに ずっと君きみに<br />\n無時不盼你 一直希望你<br />\n笑わらっていてほしくて<br />\n能一直笑口常開"},{"pid":"9983435d8079733a0587b89b35215a44ebf0e189","tid":88540,"uid":43966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:26:43.000Z","msg":"傷我或是害我都慘不過教我記得一起幸福過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"947cbb3602fddb31124eff0f4d0bce4bef229f6d","tid":88540,"uid":22580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T20:29:50.000Z","msg":"是我錯失的機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514ab2f02219025740e9e1f57bcef48074f1944f","tid":88540,"uid":67209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T21:38:31.000Z","msg":"任我多不甘 都永不超生<br />\n愈妄想幸運 愈變做貧民<br />\n<br />\n明明該意外 為何不意外<br />\n全部的意外 在預想以內<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f899c1ea15c3d9547babb18cd4dfd00c3e144bdc","tid":88540,"uid":37283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T21:53:59.000Z","msg":"幾多可笑諾言被作廢了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa659f52c51708a45beb6c3c18f045da74fe71bd","tid":88540,"uid":2809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T21:57:52.000Z","msg":"被你一貫的讚許卻不配愛下去 在你悲傷一刻必須解慰找到我樂趣<br />\n我甘願當副車也是快樂著唏噓<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c748d32d6f63d6da45b9d752bb2e741bf06073ee","tid":88540,"uid":33749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:03:17.000Z","msg":"買餸，最驚孔雀石綠<br />\n食咗有毒魚頭<br />\n行氣活血不過就會嘔"},{"pid":"6005fc23a95de0179b3be6db9e503763fbcc8b26","tid":88540,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-20T22:21:50.000Z","msg":"總不相信自己<br />\n今天失去感覺<br />\n始終總覺陌生<br />\n何時才有共嗚"},{"pid":"f00c2f